dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from an email sent by the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected where possible and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Admin 0 name and p-code fields were created and populated. 2. Reference name field created and populated. 3. Created and populated an admin 1 p-code field. Admin 1 p-codes were matched to their attributed admin 1 name. 4. Changed 6 place names from all lower case to proper case. 5. With permission from the IMO, p-codes were constructed by appending admin3 p-codes to settlement ID codes. 6. Admin names matched to names in Admin boundary candidate. 7. Values in 'popPlaceClassTitle' were changed: "Zonal Capital" was changed to 'Admin2 Capital', "Regional Capital" was changed to "Admin1 Capital", "Woreda Capital" was changed to "Admin3 Capital" and blank values were changed to null values. 8. Values in 'popPlaceClassNumber' were changed from null values based on their 'popPlaceClassTitle' value. Records with 'popPlaceClassTitle' value of 'Admin3 Capital' were given a 'popPlaceClassNumber' of "4", "Admin2 Capital"s were given 3s, "Admin1 Capital"s were given 2s, "National Capital" was given a "1" and null values were given a "5". 9. Place "Ab Ala" was given a 'popPlaceClassNumber' value of "3" and 'popPlaceClassTitle' value of "Admin2 Capital".
The following are known issues not addressed in this version:
1. Place "Bahir Dar" falls slighly outside its attributed admin2 and 3 into the hole representing Lake Tana. 2. 2 points have the same geometry: places "Shehet" and "Ab Ala". 3. 2 points named "Menge" exist in admin3 "Menge". 4. 75 admin 2 units exist in the admin boundary candidate. The populated places layer only has 48 places designated as an Admin2 Capital. 5. 2 places in admin 2 "Afder" have attribution as the capital of "Afder": "Woldya" and "Hargele". 6. 2 places in admin 2 "Borena" have attribution as the capital of "Borena": "Yabelo" and "Goba Sidamo". 7. 690 admin 3 units exist in the admin boundary candidate. The populated places layer only has 25 places designated as an Admin3 Capital.
